      "date": "2013-12-10 01:43:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nJohn, yes agreed, I will do a overall check for cfs_hash to see if there are  similar cases that can add by \"const\" and submit a separate patch, we probably should land this one right away to see if it can help on a couple of random memory corruption bugs.",
